<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.9.10">
<l>ērār poḻilcū ḻinta ḷūri lentai perumāṉaik</l>
<l>kārār puṟaviṉ maṅkai vēntaṉ kaliya ṉoliceyta</l>
<l>cīrā riṉcol mālai kaṟṟut tirivā rulakattil</l>
<l>ārā ravarē yamarark keṉṟu mamara rāvārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who wander practicing the garland of elegant, sweet words</l>
<l>Created by Kaliyaṉ, chief of Maṅkai with cloud-covered woods,</l>
<l>About the great lord, our father in Intaḷūr, encircled by beautiful groves,</l>
<l>Whoever they are in [this] world, they will always become immortals</l>
<l rend="indent">to the immortals.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
